@node "formats" "Recognized Image Formats"


 If you have the @{"Image checking option" link "options" 0} enabled, Nailer can
 recognize these image formats by reading the file's header:

 ImageFX native graphic format

 IFF/ILBM

 PNG

 JPEG

 GIF

 BMP

 TIFF


 If you have any docs explaining how to recognize any other
 image formats from their headers, please @{"let me know" link "me" 0} and I
 will try to include them.
@endnode

